{"id": "1389684619267407954", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "author_id": "534760350932008998", "author_name": "_avienna", "content": "Yep, that's right. \nThe only exception is Ramona, she didn't die before the beginning of the story but can link with the MC anyway", "timestamp": "2025-07-01T19:10:32.325000+00:00"}
{"id": "1389712454421971106", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "author_id": "551766367578095638", "author_name": "baguettesuffering", "content": "It's the case for *most* Awakeners, however this isn't the only way to become one", "timestamp": "2025-07-01T21:01:08.743000+00:00", "type": 19, "mentions": ["410521974318825473"], "reply_to": "1389679261614473356"}
{"id": "1389712704490704927", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "author_id": "551766367578095638", "author_name": "baguettesuffering", "content": "As Avienna said, Ramona for example never died, she was simply \"compatible\" with the linking process from the start", "timestamp": "2025-07-01T21:02:08.364000+00:00"}
