{"id": "1389713212395491449", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "author_id": "551766367578095638", "author_name": "baguettesuffering", "content": "Keep in mind that an Awakener isn't revived as a human, they're closer to a spirit inhabiting an artificial body in nature, at least for those who died before becoming Awakeners \n\nThose Awakeners effectively and truly *died* as humans, even if they can walk the material realm once again", "timestamp": "2025-07-01T21:04:09.458000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-07-01T21:08:20.308000+00:00"}
